Package httpclient.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutDialog
    A dialog for about menu item to show product and developer info.
    AuthPanel
    A panel that should be placed in Auth tab of request panel to define bearer token of http request.
    GuiOutputHandler
    Output handler to show request execution result in GUI form.
    HelpDialog
    A dialog for help menu item to show product help.
    HttpClientGui
    Http client GUI, a frame that will be shown as main window when program starts.
    JIconButton
    Implementation of a button that looks like an icon.
    JsonPanel
    A panel that shows a json and user can edit a it.
    NameValue
    Implementation of a name-value pair that shows a name-value and can be edited by user, if sets to be editable.
    NameValuePanel
    Implementation of a panel that have couple of name-value pairs.
    NewGroupDialog
    A dialog for new group button to add new request group.
    OptionsDialog
    A dialog for options menu item to configure some user options.
    RequestBinaryDataPanel
    Implementation of binary data panel in request panel.It contains a file chooser that selects a file as binary data to send.
    RequestPanel
    Implementation of a panel that placed at the middle of the frame and handles the user request.
    ResponseHeader
    Implementation of header panel in response tab.
    ResponsePanel
    Implementation of a panel that placed at the right side of the frame and displays the response.
    SavedRequestsPanel
    Implementation of a panel that placed at the left side of the frame and displays saved requests and request groups.
    SaveRequestDialog
    A dialog for saving new request.
